{"tid":1700717,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"致今晚意見不合嘅勇武同和理","createTime":"2019-11-08T15:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T15:52:36.000Z","uid":163448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f28c8895e3c2d3ad188d81abc42b41da333d5ac7","tid":1700717,"uid":163448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:52:36.000Z","msg":"首先，我作為一個和理非<br />\n我想向咁多位勇武道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地好多時都合作得唔好搞到你地陷入困境<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地對你地係心存感激的，你地化不可能為可能，又保護我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地和理有時又會唔明白你地，唔認同你地嘅行為。但係我地絕不割𥱊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地嘅表現唔完美但會改善！例如我地會企疏啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔好一見到警就跑得快過保特<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於勇武，兄弟爬山！各自努力！希望你地大人有大量，體諒我地有啲人真係未過到心理關口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係！每次出泥我地都大膽咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個過程我地會盡量加快去支援你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，我覺得兄弟爬山，各自努力個靈魂係不分化，不指責。係好難架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地犧牲咁多仲要不指責我地真係好難，我但求你地唔好捨棄我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地會跟上你地嘅步伐架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS 有無建議俾我地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}